506
00:37:11,166 --> 00:37:12,692
Porozmýšľaj o tom.

507
00:37:12,692 --> 00:37:15,862
Prečo by ma inak minulý rok za tebou posielal?

508
00:37:17,670 --> 00:37:19,385
